data.description: Spacious family home nestled on a tranquil lake, this home was built for a former builder, with attention to detail.  Gourmet kitchen offers solid stone counter tops, upgraded LG appliances  and a breakfast bar opening to the family room.  Volume ceilings throughout the homes with tray ceiling in master bedroom.  Overlooking the lake, this home has a huge glassed in lanai (approximately 500 square feet), which is air conditioned, but not included in living area square footage.  The home has a security system that includes surveillance cameras.  The community offers a playground for the kids, community pool, recreation center and tennis courts.  Covered Bridge is close to I-75 for an easy commute to Sarasota, St Pete and Tampa.  The Outlet Mall, restaurants, golf and more are nearby.
